low growth rate of the cumulative\nstochastic gradient, as observed empirically.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Dec 2019 22:10:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 25 Dec 2020 02:17:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-29"}
